NK029(ha)006:1: // gsum pa sgrub dbang gi chu bo las /
NK029(ha)006:3: gsum pa bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo la /
NK029(ha)006:4: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga la bsgrub dbang grags pa'i chu bo bya /
NK029(ha)006:7: dkyil 'khor las kyi rim pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:9: dang po la tshad thig dang /
NK029(ha)006:10: tshon dang bri ba'i rnam pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:22: dkyil 'khor chung tshad la khru gang dang /
NK029(ha)006:23: khru bzhi'o //'bring tshad la khru bcu gnyis dang bcu drug go //
NK029(ha)006:24: dkyil 'khor che tshad la khru nyi shu /
NK029(ha)006:26: dbang gsum pa'i dkyil 'khor gyi tshad la /
NK029(ha)006:29: de dag ni lhag pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor gyi tshad do //
NK029(ha)006:31: sbyin bdag 'byor ba che chung dang /
NK029(ha)006:32: phyag len mkhas mi mkhas gyis ji ltar rigs par bya'o //
NK029(ha)006:33: lhag par ting 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)006:36: rab tshad nam mkha'i dbyings bsam yas pa'o //
NK029(ha)006:37: de dag kyang slob dpon dgongs pa zab mi zab dang /
NK029(ha)006:38: slob bu las dag tshabs che chu nga gi dbang gis 'chad par gyur pa'i rten dang /
NK029(ha)006:39: brten pa yi dkyil 'khor bsgom pa'i dus so /
NK029(ha)006:40: gnyis pa thig la bdun la /
NK029(ha)006:42: rab gnas dang lnga ni gong sta gon gyi skabs su bshad zin la /
NK029(ha)006:46: nang bar snga bar langs ste /
NK029(ha)006:47: b+he ga ra sa ma yi /
NK029(ha)006:49: 'degs pa'i phyag rgyas sta gon gyi la rten dang /
NK029(ha)006:50: brten par bcas pa'i dkyil 'khor nam mkhar bteg la bzhugs pa bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:51: 'bras bu'i tshom bu la sogs rnams bsdus la 'gol par bzhags /
NK029(ha)006:53: ba byung la sogs pa'i dri bzang rnams dang /
NK029(ha)006:54: mgo ma yid sum bcus legs par chags chags gdab /
NK029(ha)006:57: dbang phyug kun bzang gis ting 'dzin gyi ye shes kyi thig skud /
NK029(ha)006:60: slob bu kun tu bzang mor bskyed la thig skud kyi sne mo gtad /
NK029(ha)006:63: thig skud sems kyi rang bzhin kha dog lngar brengs kyis bsam la /
NK029(ha)006:65: bdag rdo rje slob dpon che ges /
NK029(ha)006:66: slob ma che ge mo la sogs pa dbang bskur ba'i phyed du /
NK029(ha)006:67: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs gsang ba las /
NK029(ha)006:68: ches gsang ba yang gsang thugs kyi dkyil 'khor 'dus pa mdo'i dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)006:69: lhag par gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs pa'i thig 'debs pas /
NK029(ha)006:70: bdag la mthu bstan du gsol /
NK029(ha)006:73: rdo rje ye shes kyi thig gdab du gsol /
NK029(ha)006:74: phyogs bcu ma lus dus gsum gyi /
NK029(ha)006:75: rgyal ba sras bcas thams cad kun /
NK029(ha)006:76: thig gi sgra 'dis rab bskul nas /
NK029(ha)006:77: byin gyis brlabs par mdzad du gsol /
NK029(ha)006:78: badz+ra su tra sa ma ya ma tikra ma h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)006:80: gsang ba'i thad kar shar nub kyi tshangs thig gdab /
NK029(ha)006:81: de nas thig 'gros dang bcas pas /
NK029(ha)006:83: slob ma byang du phyin la /
NK029(ha)006:85: sngags gong ltar gyis tshang thig gnyis pa gdab /
NK029(ha)006:86: de nas slob dpon g.yas bskor gyis shar lho dang /
NK029(ha)006:87: slob ma nub byang du byin la gong bzhin zur thig gdab /
NK029(ha)006:88: de nas slob dpon lho nub dang /
NK029(ha)006:89: slob ma byang shar du song la gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)006:90: mdun gyi nam mkha' la ye shes lnga'i dkyil 'khor gsal bar bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:91: de nas dam tshig gi thig skud sngar bzhin thog la /
NK029(ha)006:92: ho dgongs su gsol zhes sogs dang /
NK029(ha)006:93: sarba shwa d+ha ni h+aum phata brjod la /
NK029(ha)006:94: sngar bzhin tshangs thig la sogs pa gdab pas /
NK029(ha)006:95: sku gsung thugs kyis byin brlabs dang ldan par bsam /
NK029(ha)006:96: de yang dkyil 'khor gyi lte ba nas zur thig
NK029(ha)006:97: bzhi rgyud la sor gnyis kyi tshad yod pa'i shing
NK029(ha)006:98: bus cha chen bac+wa lnga bac+wa lnga'i mtshan ma rim
NK029(ha)006:99: bzhin da bye / de nas sor gsum gyi tshad
NK029(ha)006:100: yod pa'i shing bus cha chen nyi shu rtsa bdun
NK029(ha)006:101: rtsa bdun yod pa'i mtshan ma rim bzhin bya /
NK029(ha)006:102: de nas sor drug yod pa'i shing bus cha chen bdun bdun yod pa'i mtshan ma bya /
NK029(ha)006:103: de'i steng du thig ma nor bar gdab bo //
NK029(ha)006:104: de nas tshangs thig g.yas g.yon du /
NK029(ha)006:105: phyi nang rang rang gi cha chen gyi tshad gyi cha chen gnyis gnyis gdab /
NK029(ha)006:106: de nas dkyil 'khor nang gi cha bran gdab pa ni /
NK029(ha)006:107: shar nub kyi tshangs thig gi rgyud las /
NK029(ha)006:108: dang po phyed gdab phyi ma gdab //
NK029(ha)006:109: gnyis pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)006:110: lho byang du'ang de bzhin du gdab //
NK029(ha)006:111: de nas 'phreng du gdab pa ni //
NK029(ha)006:112: gsum pa phyi'i cha phran gcig gdab //
NK029(ha)006:113: bzhi pa lha snam phyed du gdab //
NK029(ha)006:114: lnga pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)006:115: drug pa phyed gdab phyed ma gdab //
NK029(ha)006:116: bdun pa cha bzhi mnyam du gdab //
NK029(ha)006:117: brgyad pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab //
NK029(ha)006:118: de nas mu khyud bskor ba ni //
NK029(ha)006:119: cha bran lnga dang drug pa nas 'khor lo'i lte ba bskor /
NK029(ha)006:120: bcu gcig pa dang bcu gnyis pa nas rtsi bas rtse'i mu khyud bskor /
NK029(ha)006:121: cha chen bdun pa'i thog tu glang gur dang rdo rje rwa bzhi bskor /
NK029(ha)006:122: cha chen dgu pa dang bcu pa la pad rwa dang rdo rje rwa ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:123: me ri gsum ci rigs 'tshams par bskor ro //
NK029(ha)006:124: cha chen bcu gcig gi nang cha dang /
NK029(ha)006:125: bco lnga phyi ma la 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad kyi mu khyud bskor /
NK029(ha)006:126: dkyil 'khor bar ma la shar nub kyi tshangs thig gi g.yas g.yon du cha bran gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)006:127: de nas 'phred du sgo 'khyams dgu po la 'khyams dgu pa dor zhing /
NK029(ha)006:130: phyed gdab phyi ma gdab pa kho na'o //
NK029(ha)006:132: shar nub kyi tshangs thig g.yas g.yon du cha bran gong bzhin gdab /
NK029(ha)006:133: 'phred du cha chen dang po lha rnam dor /
NK029(ha)006:134: gnyis pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab pa /
NK029(ha)006:140: phyi ma gdab pa d+r+wa ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:143: bzhi pa dang lnga pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:144: drug pa gsum cha bzhi mnyam du gdab pa /
NK029(ha)006:145: rta babs snam bu brgyad dang /
NK029(ha)006:146: ka ba chen mo'i ka gzhu dang /
NK029(ha)006:147: rta babs kyi ka ba gsum ste /
NK029(ha)006:149: bdun pa dbus dor mtha' gnyis gdab /
NK029(ha)006:151: chos 'khor dang gdugs kyi thig go /
NK029(ha)006:152: de nas rta babs kyi dkyil du glang gur dang /
NK029(ha)006:154: gdugs tog gi phyi nas dur khrod dang /
NK029(ha)006:156: me ri rnams ji ltar 'os pas bskor ro //
NK029(ha)006:157: de nas ye shes kyi thig dam tshig gi thig dang /
NK029(ha)006:158: gnyis su med par ba stim /
NK029(ha)006:160: thig skud kyi lha la kun bzang /
NK029(ha)006:161: zhabs bsil bzhi bsnol gyis mchod la /
NK029(ha)006:162: thig gi lha rnams h+r+aih zhes sgra ring por brjod
NK029(ha)006:163: cing nam mkhar bteg thig skud kyi lha badz+ra mu
NK029(ha)006:164: / zhes rang bzhin gyi gnas su gshegs su gsol /
NK029(ha)006:165: gsum pa dkyil 'khor bri ba ni /
NK029(ha)006:166: dbang phyug rgyas pa'i chas su zhugs ste /
NK029(ha)006:167: sngar rab tu gnas pa'i tshon rnams ni dkyil 'khor gyi steng du nyer ldog byas la /
NK029(ha)006:170: phyag g.yas pa'i sor mo lnga la nyi ma la gnas pa'i dpa' bo 'bru lnga bsam nas /
NK029(ha)006:171: sarba pany+tsa rat+na sa ma ye h+aum h+aum /
NK029(ha)006:173: yig 'bru rnams dang tshon rtsi bsre /
NK029(ha)006:174: med na 'theb 'dzub kyis tshon sngon po 'dzin la /
NK029(ha)006:175: h+aum 'di ni chos dbyings dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)006:176: sems can khams rnams rab sgrol phyir //
NK029(ha)006:177: rim pa dang por yang dag ldan /
NK029(ha)006:178: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol /
NK029(ha)006:181: phur gyi shul du cung zhig blug /
NK029(ha)006:182: de nas rtsig pa'i sa byang shar gyi mtsham su
NK029(ha)006:183: re kha sngon po 'dzub gang ba gcig legs par
NK029(ha)006:184: bri / de'i lhag ma slar dbus kyi khung blug /'og ma kun gyi phyag len des 'gre /
NK029(ha)006:186: 'di ni me long dag pa te /
NK029(ha)006:187: sems can khams rnam rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)006:188: rim pa gnyis par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)006:189: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)006:191: tshon dmar po 'dzin la //+aah'adi ni sor rtog dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)006:192: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)006:193: rim pa gsum par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)006:194: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)006:197: s+w+aa 'di ni mnyam nyid dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)006:198: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)006:199: rim pa bzhi par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)006:200: dngos grub dam pa stsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)006:203: h+aa 'di ni bya grub dag pa ste //
NK029(ha)006:204: sems can khams rnams rab bsgral phyir //
NK029(ha)006:205: rim pa lnga par yang dag ldan //
NK029(ha)006:206: dngos grub dam pa bstsal du gsol //
NK029(ha)006:207: brjod la byang shar gyi 'tsham su re kha ljang khu bri /
NK029(ha)006:208: phud lhag dbus kyi khung bur blug la /
NK029(ha)006:209: khams lnga dag par bya ba'i don du 'byung ba
NK029(ha)006:210: rim brtsegs sgom pas don ye shes lnga tshon pa'i
NK029(ha)006:211: rtags rin po che las grub pa'i ri rab tu
NK029(ha)006:212: bsgom / ri rab de'i steng du gzhal yas khang bzhengs par bsam la /
NK029(ha)006:213: ka pa las bkab zangs gzhongs zer ba snang /
NK029(ha)006:214: thor ma song bar bya ste /
NK029(ha)006:215: phyis snang re kha 'dren pa'i dus su 'dren brtag cing /
NK029(ha)006:217: de nas zhal lung thob pa'i slob bu rnams kyis
NK029(ha)006:218: lags sor lnga la nyi ma las gnas pa'i dpa'
NK029(ha)006:219: bo 'bru lnga bkod la re kha bri ste /
NK029(ha)006:220: dbus su 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi gru chad /
NK029(ha)006:222: rtsigs pa lnga la nang nas sngon po dkar po /
NK029(ha)006:225: ljang khu lngar gyi tshon bkra dang sbrel /
NK029(ha)006:235: rta babs kyi sa la cha bran bcu gnyis yod pa la /
NK029(ha)006:237: de'i steng du gnyis la rta rkang dang chu skyes /
NK029(ha)006:238: bzhi pa la ka ba lnga pa dang drug pa la rin chen sgrom dang za ra tshags /
NK029(ha)006:239: bdun pa ka ba brgyad pa dang dgu pa la rnam 'phyang dang chun 'phyang /
NK029(ha)006:240: bcu pa la ka ba bcu gcig pa dang bcu
NK029(ha)006:241: gnyis pa la shar gnyis bu dang sna tshogs khyung
NK029(ha)006:242: mgo / rta babs bang rim bzhi byas kyang rung /
NK029(ha)006:243: de'i steng du chos 'khor gyi gdan pad+ma /
NK029(ha)006:245: g.yas g.yon du ri dwags pho mo /
NK029(ha)006:247: rta babs kyi g.yas g.yon du chu srin gyi kha nas phyung pa'i rdo rje'i ra gnyis /
NK029(ha)006:248: gdugs kyi phyi rol du pad+ma'i ra ba /
NK029(ha)006:249: rdo rje dang me ris bskor ba /
NK029(ha)006:251: 'khor lo rwa'i lte ba yi mu khyud 'khor lo'i rtsibs brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:258: lha rnam rtsig pa la sogs dkyil 'khor nang ma dang mthun la /
NK029(ha)006:260: pad+ma'i rwa ba'i tshab ma la dur khrod bri /
NK029(ha)006:261: phyi rol du ma tram 'am tu tra bri'o //
NK029(ha)006:263: dbus kyi lta ba mthing kha /
NK029(ha)006:264: mu khyud gdan nag po la mi thig dkar po /
NK029(ha)006:267: mu khyud gdan dmar po la mu thig ser po /
NK029(ha)006:272: lha rnams dang sgo phyogs mdog /
NK029(ha)006:273: mun pa dang glang gur gyi nang nag po /
NK029(ha)006:275: ka brgyan de las pogs pa /
NK029(ha)006:278: d+r+wa ba bzhi nag po la /
NK029(ha)006:279: dra ba dmar po dang dkar po'i mu thig /
NK029(ha)006:280: shar bu gzhi dmar po la shar bu dkar po dngul dam kha thur du bstan pa lta bu /
NK029(ha)006:281: mda' yab gzhi nag po la /
NK029(ha)006:282: mda' yab dkar po mchod rten nam rtse phran gyi gzugs /
NK029(ha)006:286: chos 'khor dang ri dwags ser po /
NK029(ha)006:292: rdo rje'i rwa ba gzhi nag po la rdo rje ser po /
NK029(ha)006:294: dkyil 'khor bar ma'i lte ba'i mu khyud /
NK029(ha)006:299: phyi'i mu khyud gzhi nag po la rdo rje phreng ba ser po /
NK029(ha)006:300: gru chad dang blo 'bur phyogs mdog /
NK029(ha)006:308: mun pa rnams spyi dang mthun /
NK029(ha)006:321: dkyil 'khor phyi ma'i rtsig pa la sogs nang dang 'dra ba la rta babs snam bu brgyad pa'i /
NK029(ha)006:326: sna 'phyang 'phreng ba dkar chun 'phyang ser po /
NK029(ha)006:328: sna tshogs khyung mgo de nyid do //
NK029(ha)006:337: mkha' 'gro ma brgyad la sogs dang /
NK029(ha)006:343: dum bu la sogs sna tshogs bri'o //
NK029(ha)006:344: lnga pa rnam pa 'god pa ni /
NK029(ha)006:345: lha yi gnas rnams su lha tshom rang rang gi mdog can gdan dang bcas pa 'god /
NK029(ha)006:346: dkyil 'khor nang ma zhi ba'i gzhal yas khang du bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:347: bdag nyid kun bzang yab yum du bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:350: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las kun bzang yab yum bton la /
NK029(ha)006:355: a a a badz+ra sa man+ta /
NK029(ha)006:357: de bzhin du mi bskyod pa yab yum bton la /
NK029(ha)006:358: tsaka li la stim zhing h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig /
NK029(ha)006:362: de bzhin du rtsibs bzhi la rigs bzhi yab yum
NK029(ha)006:363: rtsibs mchan bzhi la nang gi sems dpa' yab yum
NK029(ha)006:364: / gru chad bzhi la phyi'i sems dpa' yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:365: lha snam la thub pa drug /
NK029(ha)006:366: sgo bzhi la sgo ba yab yum bzhi /
NK029(ha)006:367: gsang gnas nas bton tsaka li la ba stim pa 'god do //
NK029(ha)006:369: de'i steng du khro ba'i gzhal yas khang bskyed la /
NK029(ha)006:370: bdag che mchog du bskyed la /
NK029(ha)006:372: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer las /
NK029(ha)006:373: che mchog yab yum bton la /
NK029(ha)006:374: tsa ka li la stim la /
NK029(ha)006:375: a kra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)006:377: dbus mi skyod pa'i mdun du 'god /
NK029(ha)006:378: badz+ra he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:379: badz+ra sh+ri he ru ka h+aum /
NK029(ha)006:380: badz+ra kro ti shwo ri h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)006:381: dbus su che mchog yab yum gyi mdun du dgod /
NK029(ha)006:382: rigs bzhi he ru ka yab yum rang rang gi sngags kyis phyogs bzhi'i rtsibs bzhi la 'god /
NK029(ha)006:383: lung gi he ru ka yab yum bzhi /
NK029(ha)006:384: rang rang gi sngags kyis mtshams kyis rtsibs bzhi la bkod /
NK029(ha)006:385: koo ri ma la sogs gnas kyi ma mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:386: rang rang gi sngags kyi gru chad bzhi /
NK029(ha)006:388: phra men ma brgyad rang rang gi sngags kyis 'khyams dang po la dgod /
NK029(ha)006:389: 'khyams gnyis pa la spor ma brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:392: sgo bzhi dzah h+aum bam ho bzhi las /
NK029(ha)006:394: sh+r+ai badz+ra mu ka ra ya ya na ma /
NK029(ha)006:395: sh+r+ai badz+ra gan+d+ha pra dz+wa la ya na ma /
NK029(ha)006:396: sh+r+ai badz+ra ra ka sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK029(ha)006:397: sh+r+ai badz+ra kha tam ga pra dz+wa la ya ya na ma /
NK029(ha)006:400: b+h+yoo nyi shu rtsa brgyad las dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:401: rang rang gi sngags kyis bkod /
NK029(ha)006:402: de yan chad ni khrag mthung rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor zhes bya /
NK029(ha)006:403: 'khyams bzhi pa 'phrin las myur mgyogs kyi dal la /
NK029(ha)006:405: sum bcu rtsa gnyis las mkha' 'gro ma sum bcu rtsa gnyis /
NK029(ha)006:409: h+aum bdun las ma mo bdun /
NK029(ha)006:410: ting bzhi las sring mo bzhi /
NK029(ha)006:415: sgrol byed ging gi dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)006:418: ging ka ra ha ha ru lu ru lu b+h+yoo bac+wa brgyad kyis 'god /
NK029(ha)006:419: bar bar 'khyams bdun pa khro bo rol pa'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK029(ha)006:422: kro d+ha kro d+hi h+aum drug cu 'god /
NK029(ha)006:423: 'khyams brgyad pa mgyogs 'gro yid kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)006:424: shar du dza drug cu las dung gi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)006:425: b+ha na b+ha na ang gu sha dza /
NK029(ha)006:427: lhor h+aum drug bcu las gser gyi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)006:428: ha la ha la pa sha h+aum /
NK029(ha)006:432: zangs kyi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)006:433: gardza gardza spo ta bam drug bcu 'god /
NK029(ha)006:434: byang phyogs su ho drug bcu las /
NK029(ha)006:435: lcags kyi pho nya drug bcu /
NK029(ha)006:436: pa tsa pa tsa gan d+he ho drug cu 'god /
NK029(ha)006:437: 'khyams dgu pa dang lnga pa dam tshig rgya mtsho'i dkyil 'khor te /
NK029(ha)006:438: lnga pa gong du song nas dgu pa la ma drug bcu las /
NK029(ha)006:439: 'og phyogs kyi ma mo drug bcu /
NK029(ha)006:440: ma ma shwa ra h+aum drug bcu 'god /
NK029(ha)006:441: 'khyams bcu pa la rigs 'dzin rtsal 'chang gi dkyil 'khor /
NK029(ha)006:442: rigs 'dzin brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams /
NK029(ha)006:443: ma h+aa gu ru sha ri ram /
NK029(ha)006:445: bla ma dang tsa ka li dbyer med dgod do //
NK029(ha)006:446: de nas bum pa 'god pa ni /
NK029(ha)006:447: khro bo gsang ba'i bum pa ste /
NK029(ha)006:451: zhi ba'i bum pa lnga rgyal theb la sog pas 'dzin /
NK029(ha)006:453: h+aum bum pa ma lags rgyal po lags //
NK029(ha)006:454: rgyal po sngags kyis btab nas kyang //
NK029(ha)006:455: rgyal po chen por mnga' gsol kyis //
NK029(ha)006:456: rgyal po'i tshul du bzhugs su gsol //
NK029(ha)006:458: sngags lta gon gyi skabs bzhin /
NK029(ha)006:461: rdo rje dang bcas pa sngar lta gon gyi skabs ltar legs par bkod /
NK029(ha)006:464: dbang rdzas la sogs rnams dang /
NK029(ha)006:472: 'phan bla res la sogs mchod par 'os pa'i rgyan kun gyis legs par brgyan par bya'o //
NK029(ha)006:473: de nas dkyil 'khor la sogs de rnams la byin phabs te /
NK029(ha)006:474: spos dkar gyis dud pa btang nas /
NK029(ha)006:475: rol mo'i sgra sna tshogs bsgrag cing /
NK029(ha)006:476: rnal 'byor pa pho rnams kyis chas gos bzang po
NK029(ha)006:477: dang bcas pas has sti g.yab cing dkyil 'khor bskor
NK029(ha)006:478: / mo rnams chas gos bzang po dang bcas pas phreng bas g.yab cing /
NK029(ha)006:480: h+aum nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i 'jig rten nas /
NK029(ha)006:481: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK029(ha)006:482: rgyas pa'i bsrung mar gyur pa'i dam tshig can //
NK029(ha)006:483: mchod do bla ma rnams la skyabs su mchi //
NK029(ha)006:484: h+aum mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK029(ha)006:485: bcom ldan che mchog khro rgyal 'khor dang bcas //
NK029(ha)006:486: sngags tshig bshugs kyi brda' yis spyan 'dren gyis //
NK029(ha)006:487: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pas g.yab dor na //
NK029(ha)006:488: dpal chen yab yum thugs dam rjes dgongs la //
NK029(ha)006:489: thugs dam brda' la dgongs te gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)006:490: h+aum chos nyid bde ba chen po'i sku byung ba //
NK029(ha)006:491: bcom ldan che mchog yab yum gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)006:492: dur khrod dreg pa'i tshogs rnams 'joms mdzad pa //
NK029(ha)006:493: rgyud lung khro rgyal yab yum ye shes 'bar ma
NK029(ha)006:494: brgyad kyi ke ri khro mo brgyad po chos nyid
NK029(ha)006:495: mkha' ltar dag pa'i seng ha phra men brgyad po
NK029(ha)006:496: gshegs 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod nang shod du
NK029(ha)006:497: // spor ma gsang yum tshogs rnams tshad med bzhi
NK029(ha)006:498: rdzogs gsang ba'i rta gdong sgo ma 'khor bcas dam
NK029(ha)006:499: tshig lhun gyis grub pa'i dbang phyug ming sring 'khor
NK029(ha)006:500: bcas zhe sdang 'bar ba thugs kyi khro rgyal srin
NK029(ha)006:501: po 'khor dur khrod 'bar ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor
NK029(ha)006:502: // nas // mkha' 'gro sum bcu rtsa gnyis sgrol
NK029(ha)006:503: byed 'bar ba las kyi rdo rje ging chen 'khor
NK029(ha)006:504: bcas ci bgyis ba ka' nyan las kyi pho nya
NK029(ha)006:505: sde mo 'khor bcas las rnams yongs su grub pa'i
NK029(ha)006:506: ye shes ma mo'i tshogs rnams sdom pa sa la
NK029(ha)006:508: rig 'dzin rtsal 'chang 'khor bcas gshegs su gsol //
NK029(ha)006:509: deng gi gnas mchog dur drod tshogs re spro /
NK029(ha)006:510: ban+d+ha gsar snying tshogs ni rdza ltar lhag /
NK029(ha)006:511: keng rus gsar rnying tshogs ni ri ltar spungs //
NK029(ha)006:512: rak+ta gsar rnying tshogs ni mtsho ltar ba skyil //
NK029(ha)006:513: mam sa gsar rnying tshogs ni thang du brdal //
NK029(ha)006:514: zhing chen gsar snying tshogs ni rlung ltar dpungs //
NK029(ha)006:515: byang chub sems kyi tshogs ni gangs ltar chags //
NK029(ha)006:516: brgyan cha gsar rnying tshogs ni sprin ltar gtibs //
NK029(ha)006:517: ta na ga na'i tshogs ni dbyings na rol //
NK029(ha)006:518: rdo rje mched lcam lha dang lha mo ra rol //
NK029(ha)006:519: ma mo mkha' 'gro'i tshogs ni nam mkhar 'thibs //
NK029(ha)006:520: rnal 'byor longs spyod che la spyan 'dren na //
NK029(ha)006:521: thugs dam brda' la dgongs ste gshegs nas kyang //
NK029(ha)006:522: dkyil 'khor chen po 'di la byin phob la //
NK029(ha)006:523: bsgrub pa'i rtags dang mtshan ma bstan nas kyang //
NK029(ha)006:524: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi sid+d+hi stsol //
NK029(ha)006:525: badz+ra sa ma ya sid+d+hi phem phem //
NK029(ha)006:526: badz+ra yo gi ni sa ma ya dzah badz+ra a be sha ya a a /
NK029(ha)006:527: ces brjod pas lha tshogs de rnams dkyil 'khor dang tsa ka li'i thog du byon te /
NK029(ha)006:529: pra b+he shas gnyis su med par thim pas lha rnams gzi byin dang ldan par bsam mo /
NK029(ha)006:530: drug pa rab gnas la brgyad de /
NK029(ha)006:531: sngon du bya ba'i cho ga dang /
NK029(ha)006:532: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal ba skyed pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:533: rang bzhin gyis dkyil 'khor spyan drangs nas bstim pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:534: dbang po skyon gsal gyi chos bdun bya ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:535: me long phul la chu bdun gyis sku khrus gsol zhing sku phyi ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:536: che ba'i yon tan dang rgyan cha rnams kyi dbang bskur zhing mnga' gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:537: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rdzogs par phul ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:538: bden pa'i byin brlabs dmigs shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba te /
NK029(ha)006:539: de la yon bdag la sogs pas bskor ba bya
NK029(ha)006:540: zhing phyag 'tshal nas mi 'bral zhing mngon du gyur
NK029(ha)006:541: cig / ces smon lam gdab po /
NK029(ha)006:550: bcom ldan 'das dpal kun tu bzang po la phyag 'a tshal lo //
NK029(ha)006:551: gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i zhi khro rnam pa gnyis la /
NK029(ha)006:552: rnal 'byor pa rgan po rnams kyi don ched du lta ba dang rtogs pa gsal ba dang //
NK029(ha)006:555: 'bras bu mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)006:556: rgyud las lung du bsgyur ste /
NK029(ha)006:557: de las rgyud ni gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor mngon du bris /
NK029(ha)006:559: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs nas /
NK029(ha)006:561: tshe gcig gi sangs rgyas pa ni 'gro don las kyi dkyil 'khor ro /
NK029(ha)006:562: lung gi gzugs brnyan gyi dal dngos su mi dgos ste /
NK029(ha)006:563: lus la lha bkod yid kyi gsal btab nas zhes byung bas /
NK029(ha)006:564: lus la lha bkod nas snying po bzlas pa tsam gyis /
NK029(ha)006:565: sku gsal bar bsgom pa ni las thams cad kyang
NK029(ha)006:566: ma tshon byed kyi sangs rgyas pa ni bdag don
NK029(ha)006:567: lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro /
NK029(ha)006:568: de la lung du gyur pas /
NK029(ha)006:572: tshogs dang gtor ma'i lung dang /
NK029(ha)006:576: bdag lus kyi phyogs bzhi mtshams brgyad steng 'og gnyis te bcur nyi dkyi la bcu dang /
NK029(ha)006:577: phyogs skyong pho mo bcu'i steng /
NK029(ha)006:578: h'u ka ra badz+ra ma h+aa kro d+ha h+aum h+aum phata /
NK029(ha)006:579: zhes sogs rtsa ba'i sngags bcu brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:580: khro bo chen po yab yum bcu /
NK029(ha)006:581: stod zhal gsum phyag drug tu bsgom la /
NK029(ha)006:582: smad lcags kyi phur pa zur gsum gyis thal phyur bar bsgoms la /
NK029(ha)006:584: mtshams 'dir thams cad ma 'dus pa med do //
NK029(ha)006:585: sman lung ni pad+ma ban+d+hara bdud rtsi dpa' bor sbyangs la /
NK029(ha)006:589: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis ma bskyed rdzogs pa'i tshul du sku bskyed la /
NK029(ha)006:590: de bdud rtsi chen por byin gyis brlabs te zhu ba la 'di brjod do //
NK029(ha)006:592: tshogs gtogs lung rgyud chen po nas 'byung ba ltar brlabs te 'di brjod do //
NK029(ha)006:594: b+h+rum bi sha bi shud+d+he brjod pa /
NK029(ha)006:595: phyi snod thams cad sna tshogs dag pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK029(ha)006:596: rang bzhin rnam par dag cing 'dus ma byas pa'i pho brang chos kyi dbyings /
NK029(ha)006:597: dbang chen yu ma lnga'i mkha' klong nas /
NK029(ha)006:598: dus gsum du yangs dog dang /
NK029(ha)006:601: mtho dman med pa'i dbus na /
NK029(ha)006:602: bdag gi lus sems kyi rgyal po chen por lhun gyis grub pa /
NK029(ha)006:603: lha'i dkyil 'khor du ye nas yin pas bdag gi spyi gtsug /
NK029(ha)006:604: dz+nya na tsakra dz+wa la ma d+ha la zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:605: ye shes kyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi pa /
NK029(ha)006:606: 'bar ba'i zer dang bcas par gyur pa'i steng du /
NK029(ha)006:607: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas phung po lnga las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)006:608: bzhugs gnas bdag gi da bu'i gtsug 'khor lo'i dbus su /
NK029(ha)006:613: phyogs bzhi la glang po dang /
NK029(ha)006:617: phyogs bzhi dbus dang lngar bkod pa'i /
NK029(ha)006:618: dbus kyi seng ge'i steng du /
NK029(ha)006:619: h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika ces brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:620: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog dang phyag mtshan
NK029(ha)006:621: rgyan dang cha lugs rgyud dang mthun par gsal zhing
NK029(ha)006:622: bskyed / de bzhin du tshangs ma la 'khor lo'i steng du rnam par snang mdzad /
NK029(ha)006:623: rna ba g.yas pa'i steng du rin 'byung /
NK029(ha)006:625: rna ba g.yon par gdon mi za ba rnams rtsa sngags brjod pa tsam gyis sku gsal gyis bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:626: yum chen mo lnga don gyis 'byung lngas grub kyang /
NK029(ha)006:627: rdo rje sems dpa'i mdun du mum d+ha du shwa ri zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:628: kun tu bzang mo zhal gcig phyag gnyis rgyan dang cha lugs gtso bo cha mthun par bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:629: de bzhin du yum lnga char yang gtso bo'i mdun du thabs shes rab kyi tshul du sgom /
NK029(ha)006:630: sems dpa' brgyad rnams shes bzhi /
NK029(ha)006:631: dbang po bzhi las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)006:633: mig g.yas pa la k+shi hi ra tsa ya zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:634: sa'i snying po wal gyis bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:635: de bzhin rna ba g.yas badz+ra pa ni /
NK029(ha)006:642: de bzhin du sems ma brgyad kyang yul bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)006:644: sems dpa' brgyad kyi mdun du rtsa snying brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:645: thabs shes rab tshul du gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:646: phrag gong g.yas g.yon ste ke mdun rgyab du khro bo bzhi dang /
NK029(ha)006:647: khro mo bzhi thabs dang shes rab kyi tshul du gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:648: dpral ba dang lce steng snying khar /
NK029(ha)006:651: zhabs mthil drug du thub pa drug rim gyis bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:653: sog phrag tu bzang mo la sogs pa rtsa ba'i
NK029(ha)006:654: sngags bzlas pa tsam gyis sku gsal bar bskyed nas
NK029(ha)006:655: / ye shes lnga dang ldan pas dbang bskur zhing /
NK029(ha)006:656: sku gsung thugs byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK029(ha)006:658: sems gsal btab pa de rang bzhin gyi sangs rgyas pa yin kyang /
NK029(ha)006:659: shes rab zhan pas rang bzhin dang /
NK029(ha)006:660: ting 'dzin gnyis su med par rtogs par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)006:661: spyan drangs pa yang rgyud ltar tshigs bcad kyis spyan drangs mi dgos te /
NK029(ha)006:662: rtsa ba'i sngags kyi spyan drangs pas /
NK029(ha)006:663: thams cad de'i ngang du ma 'dus pa med pas /
NK029(ha)006:664: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wa na h+aum badz+ra d+h+rig mum du shwa ri /
NK029(ha)006:665: dzahh+aum bam hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam zhes /
NK029(ha)006:666: kun bzang yab yum yan chad brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:667: rang bzhin ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor dang bcas pa byon par bsam mo //
NK029(ha)006:668: gnyis su med pas tha mi dad cing dbyer med par phyag ba tsal ba yang h+aum badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK029(ha)006:669: na mo mum d+ha tu shwo ri na mo //
NK029(ha)006:672: gnyis su med pa'i 'dres pa chen por phyag tshal lo //
NK029(ha)006:673: dam tshig sems dpa' dang ye shes sems dpa' dbyer
NK029(ha)006:674: med pas chos kyi sku rtag pa chen po 'gyur
NK029(ha)006:675: ba med par brtan zhing mi 'gyur ba bzhugs su
NK029(ha)006:676: gsol ba ni / d+harma k+aa ya badz+ra d+h+rika m+au d+ha tu shwa ri /
NK029(ha)006:677: sti ra badz+ra su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK029(ha)006:678: zhes brtan zhing mi 'gyur bar bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK029(ha)006:679: mchod cing 'phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK029(ha)006:681: de nas bsgrub cing mthar phyin par bya ba ni /
NK029(ha)006:682: lus kyi sgul bskyod thams cad dam tshig gi phyag
NK029(ha)006:683: rgya yin par shes par byas la mi 'gyur bar
NK029(ha)006:684: bsgrub pa dang / ngag gi bzlas brjod thams cad
NK029(ha)006:685: chos nyid kyi snying po yin par rtogs par byas
NK029(ha)006:686: bsgrub pa dang / la / mi 'da' bar bsgrub pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:687: sems kyi dran rtog thams cad ting 'dzin gyi rang bzhin yin par yid ches par byas la /
NK029(ha)006:689: chos thams cad lha dal gyi rang bzhin du mi 'grub pa med do //
NK029(ha)006:690: de'i don mthar phyin par bya ba'i 'phrin las mdzad do //
NK029(ha)006:691: zhi ba'i don thams cad ma 'dus pa med do //
NK029(ha)006:692: zhi ba'i lung gi sgom khog rdzogs so /
NK029(ha)006:693: he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK029(ha)006:694: khro bo'i lung du bsgyur ba la /
NK029(ha)006:695: 'di ni ye shes lha'i lung ste /
NK029(ha)006:696: de yang dang po las dang bya ba ci dang ci rtsam kyang /
NK029(ha)006:697: yi dam lha ma bsgom na mi 'grub ste /
NK029(ha)006:699: lha spangs dge spyad don med 'gyur /
NK029(ha)006:701: bdag nyid ma h+aa yo ga'i gzhung ltar /
NK029(ha)006:702: ting 'dzin rnam gsum gyis shes pa'i rgyud dag par sbyangs nas /
NK029(ha)006:703: cho ga gsum gyis lha sku phyag rgya gsal bar bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:704: cho 'phrul chen po bzhi dang ldan par bsgom nas /
NK029(ha)006:705: de nyid lung gi 'bras bu mthar phyin par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)006:707: e yam rak+ta ke ram zhes pas /
NK029(ha)006:708: rlung dang nam mkha' sha khrag gi rgya mtsho dang /
NK029(ha)006:709: keng rus kyi ri rab dang /
NK029(ha)006:710: dur khrod kyi me ri sna tshogs pa 'bar ba'i mkha' klong yul lnga'i dal gyi steng du /
NK029(ha)006:712: b+h+rum bi shwa bi shud+d+he dz+nya na tsakra su raya man+dala de ba tish+tha ti ra bam zhes pas /
NK029(ha)006:713: stong gsum khams gsum kyi srid gsum gyi gnas 'di
NK029(ha)006:714: nyid ye nas rnam dag dur khrod kyi gzhal yas
NK029(ha)006:715: khang rgya mtha' dbus med pa /
NK029(ha)006:716: dur khrod kyis thod rus rnam pa sna tshogs pas
NK029(ha)006:717: rtsigs pa lha'i rgyal po dregs pa can bdud kyi
NK029(ha)006:718: rgyal po'i gdung byas pa ti ra chung ngu mang
NK029(ha)006:720: ru tra dregs pa'i khog pas gzhal yas gang gi dbyibs byas pa /
NK029(ha)006:721: dur khrod kyi brgyan gzhung du ma dang mthun pas /
NK029(ha)006:722: ye shes kyi me ri smug nag 'bar ba'i nang du /
NK029(ha)006:725: don snying lngas kha dog lnga'i tshon phye /
NK029(ha)006:726: nyi ma 'khor lo lte ba la /
NK029(ha)006:727: long ka zur bzhi 'khor lo rtsibs /
NK029(ha)006:728: nu ma byang chub kyi 'phrin las du 'brel ba las /
NK029(ha)006:729: he ru ka don gyi ye shes kyi rtsa dgu h+aum dgu las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)006:730: bdag gi lus la bsgom pa ni /
NK029(ha)006:732: ma h+aa a khra sh+ri he ru ka zhes brjod pas /
NK029(ha)006:733: bdag gi lus nyid che mchog he ru ka yab yum mthing nag zhal gsum phyag drug par bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:735: yum dgu dur drod kyi klong dgu las grub kyang
NK029(ha)006:736: lus kyi g.yon shes rab kyi rang bzhin yin pas
NK029(ha)006:737: / a kra kro ti shwa ri sgom /
NK029(ha)006:738: tsit+ta rtsa dgu khams gsum sa dgu rang byung ye
NK029(ha)006:739: shes su gsal ba he ru ka yab yum bac+wa
NK029(ha)006:741: tsi ta gu h+ya he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:742: tsi ta'i dkyil 'khor du sa nu he ru ka yab yum sgom /
NK029(ha)006:743: 'di rnams kyi sku mdog phyag mtshan ma ha su ka dang mthun /
NK029(ha)006:744: 'tsher pa las badz+ra he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:745: de bzhin du mchin pa la bud+ha he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:746: grod pa la rat+na yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:747: glo ba la pad ma he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:748: mkhris pa la karma he ru ka yab yum sgom /
NK029(ha)006:749: ma mo brgyad dang 'phra med brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:750: dur drod kyi yul brgyad dang gnas brgyad las grub kyang /
NK029(ha)006:751: lus la bkod na g.yas kyi rtsibs ma brgyad la ma mo brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:752: g.yon gyi rtsib ma brgyad la 'phra men brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:753: phrag g.yas su rak+sha he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:754: phrag g.yon du sa nu he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:755: barla g.yon du gu h+ya he ru ka yab yum /
NK029(ha)006:756: barla g.yas du yak+sha he ru ka yab yum bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:757: lus kyi mdun rgyab phyogs mtshams brgyad du spor ma brgyad /
NK029(ha)006:758: de yang brgyad las smug nag mdung dang /
NK029(ha)006:759: ral gri thog pa bskyed do //
NK029(ha)006:760: yan lag bzhi la phata bzhi la sgo ba bzhi /
NK029(ha)006:761: sgal tshig nyer brgyad la b+h+yo las dbang phyug nyer brgyad smug nag tri shul can bskyed do //
NK029(ha)006:762: rus mgo la h+aum mthing nag drug bcu las khro
NK029(ha)006:763: bo khro mo thod khrag rdo rje dkrugs te gsol
NK029(ha)006:764: ba drug bcu ru bskyed do //
NK029(ha)006:765: so sum bcu rtsa gnyis la e so gnyis las
NK029(ha)006:766: da ki so gnyis smug nag gri thogs pa bskyed
NK029(ha)006:767: do // rtsa sum brgya drug bcu la bum sum
NK029(ha)006:768: brgya drug bcu las pho nya sum brgya drug bcu
NK029(ha)006:769: thod khrag rdo rje dkrugs te gsol ba bskyed /
NK029(ha)006:770: lte'u rtsibs bac+wo brgyad la ha las ging bac+wa brgyad
NK029(ha)006:771: gri dang thod pa thogs pa dmar nag bskyed do
NK029(ha)006:772: // nam tshim rtsibs ma bzhi la gsang ba'i yum bzhi bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:773: gzugs drug mgo dang bdun la ma mo chen mo bdun bsgom /
NK029(ha)006:774: ne'u seg bzhi la sring mo bzhi bsgo /
NK029(ha)006:775: 'di rnams rtsa sngags bzlas pa tsam gyis bskyed do //
NK029(ha)006:776: rdzogs pa'i tshul du bskyed do //
NK029(ha)006:777: rtsa ba'i sngags dang sku mdog phyag mtshan dbang gi skabs su gsal lo //
NK029(ha)006:779: ba spu bye ba bzhi khri bzhi 'bum ni /
NK029(ha)006:781: yang sprul bzhi khri bzhi 'bum yang nag mo kha shog can gyi tshogs dang /
NK029(ha)006:784: sgrol byed la sogs pa sprul pa'i phyag nyan rnam par sna tshogs par bsgom pas /
NK029(ha)006:785: 'di ltar snang ba'i chos thams cad bdag gi lus
NK029(ha)006:786: dang phung po dang khams dang skye mched du 'dus
NK029(ha)006:787: la / de thams cad dkyil 'khor gyi lha'i rang bzhin du sangs rgyas pas /
NK029(ha)006:788: 'di ltar bsgom na sangs rgya ba las /
NK029(ha)006:789: 'phrin las lung gis ma zin pa phal ni /
NK029(ha)006:790: ltung grib dang gol sa che bas /
NK029(ha)006:791: thar pa'i gnas su mi 'gyur zhing 'gro ba'i don mi rdzogs pas /
NK029(ha)006:792: 'di ltar bsgom na lta spyod sgrub pa dang gsum gyis don ma 'dus pa med do //
NK029(ha)006:793: de nas gang zag gsar bu yid ches par bya ba'i phyir /
NK029(ha)006:794: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dal rtsa ba'i sngags kyis spyan drangs la /
NK029(ha)006:795: mtshan brjod cing phyag 'tshal bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK029(ha)006:796: mchod pa la sogs pa dang /
NK029(ha)006:797: 'phrin las snga ma bzhin du brjod nas /
NK029(ha)006:798: bzlas brjod kyi yan lag ni /
